<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٤٨٢ -<span class="c5"> ومنها:</span> قُتِلَ زَوْجُ سُبَيْعَةَ فَوَضَعَتْ بَعْدَ مَوْتِهِ بِأَرْبَعِينَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٧٩⦘ لَيْلَةً فَخُطِبَتْ فَأَنْكَحَهَا - صلى الله عليه وسلم - <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) البخاري (٤٩٠٩).</p> </div>